Countdown Jerusalem (Christian Movie)


Society is destabilized, and as a series of catastrophic disasters nudge the world ever closer to Armageddon, a journalist sets out on search of her daughter in this apocalyptic thriller in the tradition of The Omega Code and Left Behind.

Runtime: 94 mins
Language: English
Year: 2009
Quality: 9/10
Format: avi format 

